precis:
Authority (a) to establish an AGRICULTURAL INCOME DISASTER ASSISTANCE
PROGRAM, (b) to make payments to farmers facing a serious decline in their
1998 and 1999 income due to circumstances beyond their control, and (c) to
enter into a cost-sharing AGREEMENT with all the provinces in connection
with this program.
